'''Matsugasaki Cave Tomb Cluster''' (松ヶ崎横穴墓群) is a {{ill|cave tomb cluster|ja|横穴墓群遺跡|3=横穴墓|1=Cave tomb|lt=Cave tombs|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/cave tomb cluster|13=User:Immanuelle/Cave tomb|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} dating from the [[:en:Kofun period|Kofun period]] to the early [[:en:Nara period|Nara period]], located in {{ill|Kōnandai, Yokohama|ja|港南台|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōnandai, Yokohama|qq=}}, [[:en:Kōnan-ku, Yokohama|Kōnan-ku, Yokohama]], [[:en:Yokohama|Yokohama]], [[:en:Kanagawa Prefecture|Kanagawa Prefecture]]. It is part of the {{ill|Itachigawa Basin Rock-Cut Tombs|ja|㹨川流域横穴墓群|ja|㹨川流域横穴墓群|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itachigawa Basin Rock-Cut Tombs|qq=}} and has been registered as a {{ill|Yokohama City Registered Cultural Property|ja|横浜市登録地域文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokohama City Registered Cultural Property|qq=}} (Regional Historic Site).<ref>{{Cite web|language=ja|url=https://www.townnews.co.jp/0112/2015/11/26/309854.html|title=港南台 横穴墓群が地域文化財に|website=Town News Kōnan & Sakae Ward Edition|date=2015-11-26|accessdate=2020-07-22}}</ref>
